name: Zenft Garden Society / Twitter Banner Templates
description:
These are pre-configured Twitter banner templates and in-feed cards made by 8ncient Gardener for the Zenft Garden Society.


Please watch the accompanying Instructional Video to get started.


There are templates for each background as well as 1, 2, and 4 bonsai configurations.


Please reach out to me in Discord for any help or changes.
